Company Background

R K Pareek & Co. (the firm) is founded by CA Rishi Kant Pareek and CA Rachita Jain in the year 2012. R K Pareek & Co. is equipped with experienced professional team of chartered accountants and having its offices at Jaipur, Kota, Jodhpur and Hyderabad.
